%% L2 to L1 Withdrawal Flow (SDK)
sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant L2 as L2 (L2MessageService)
    participant Coord as Coordinator
    participant L1 as L1 (LineaRollup)

    User->>L2: withdraw()
    L2->>L2: MessageSent event<br/>Rolling hash update
    L2->>Coord: Event detected
    Coord->>L1: finalization with proof
    User->>L2: getL2ToL1MessageStatus()
    L2-->>User: CLAIMABLE
    User->>L2: getMessageProof()
    L2-->>User: proof
    User->>L1: claimOnL1(proof)
    L1-->>User: ETH received
